Comment: 10,0:08:56.60,0:09:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am searching for a certain book—\Nan ancient tome regarding the Nine Olde Witches.
Comment: 10,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not find it in the library, so I wondered\Nif you might know of its whereabouts.
Comment: 10,0:09:08.26,0:09:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for a book about ancient magic, the place to search is Luna Nova's reference archives.
Comment: 10,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You need special permission to gain access.
Comment: 10,0:09:18.64,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust that you will use this responsibly. {before someone complains this isn't what the line says at all, the two lines together basically give off these words}{## can't tell obviously, but isn't there some way to reproduce whatever's said without losing the quality of the TL? something like "I believe I won't see my trust misplaced in you" or something}{not even that, the lines are 'only special people may enter//I give you permission'}
Comment: 10,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am most grateful.
Comment: 10,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Diana. {that was too many things}
Comment: 10,0:09:27.11,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go when the moon is high in the sky.
Comment: 10,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight is a blue moon.
Comment: 10,0:09:36.45,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic of the blue moon may reveal a secret to you.
Comment: 10,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Phaidoari Afairrynghor.
Comment: 10,0:09:49.09,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}That which is dreamed cannot be grasped.
Comment: 10,0:09:51.82,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}But work towards it, day after day, \Nand you will find it in your hands.
Comment: 10,0:09:57.65,0:10:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Come to think of it, tonight is the blue moon.
Comment: 10,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Comment: 10,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Comment: 10,0:10:14.85,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Comment: 10,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Hey, do you know what a blue moon is?
Comment: 10,0:10:20.74,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}When there are two full moons in a month,\Nthe second one is called a blue moon.
Comment: 10,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}It only happens once every few years.
Comment: 10,0:10:31.37,0:10:35.35,Default,,15,15,0,,{\fax-0.2}"An apparition of yore, emerging but during a blue moon—"{## i want to avoid apparition appearing}
Comment: 10,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Though hard to please, knows of the past, present, and future.
Comment: 10,0:10:40.78,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing on its boundless knowledge, it will answer the questions of those who can appease it."{## all questions?}{no}
Comment: 10,0:10:48.20,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer... the questions.{## all questions?}
Comment: 10,0:10:54.40,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight is my last chance for the next several years.
Comment: 10,0:10:58.21,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The apparition will show up in the Blue Moon Abyss.{## akko-poi}
Comment: 10,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}"At the base of Luna Nova's New Moon Tower,
Comment: 10,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}underneath the chapel, lies a cave known as the Blue Moon Abyss.
Comment: 10,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}That is where the apparition will come forth.
Comment: 10,0:12:32.05,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Legends say the entrance to the cave only opens on the night of a blue moon."
Comment: 10,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The cave's entrance...
Comment: 10,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This leads to the Blue Moon Abyss...{## this what? stairway would be nice but that's not it}
Comment: 10,0:13:29.14,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}"There exists a hidden art that witches have passed down from the megalithic ages. {a lot of things are said right here. it kind of puts the age or era of megaliths all together for oen, but more importantly the word "ougi" is used. it's really hard to translate, but I'm going with hidden art for now}{## spooky ougi}{it actually reminds me of tales of symphonia}
Comment: 10,0:13:34.50,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}The hidden art known as the Grand Triskelion\Nhas the power to change the world." {you can see what a triskelion is. we have no idea of what form this takes, so 'hidden art' may or may not be the best word here}{## i'll take it}
Comment: 10,0:13:41.95,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the seventh century, the Nine Olde Witches \Nsealed the Grand Triskelion within Arcturus. {ha ha, you can see her speak in this part}
Comment: 10,0:13:49.95,0:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the staff bearing the seven stars, \NClaiomh Solais, may break the seal. {and finally we get the origin of the magic}
Comment: 10,0:13:56.01,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To use it, one must speak the seven Words of Arcturus." {kotonoha is an interesting and fancy way of saying words, and it deserves a capital. although each word is actually several, but phrase doesn't sound as good}
Comment: 10,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The seven Words?
Comment: 10,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu Orfei, Aude Fraetor.
Comment: 10,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Strive for your ideal place. {bd}
Comment: 10,0:14:22.53,0:14:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The day she arrived at Luna Nova,\NAkko revived the first Word.
Comment: 10,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}The staff!{## this was re-recorded i guess?}
Comment: 10,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Noctu Orfei!
Comment: 10,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Noctu... Orfei!
Comment: 10,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Aude!
Comment: 10,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Aude!
Comment: 10,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Fraetor!
Comment: 10,0:14:44.86,0:14:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Shiny Arc!
Comment: 10,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oblivious of the truth...
Comment: 10,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot might've been here too.
Comment: 10,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come?
Comment: 10,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come?
Comment: 10,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone...
Comment: 10,0:15:37.19,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come?
Comment: 10,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Comment: 10,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet... at last.
Comment: 10,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your magic show!
Comment: 10,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Luna Nova to become a witch like you.
Comment: 10,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I become more like you?
Comment: 10,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You are who I dream of being!
Comment: 10,0:16:22.08,0:16:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you realized it by now?
Comment: 10,0:16:28.12,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you reach out,\Nyour dream will never come true. {parallel episode 1}
Comment: 10,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.{## i appreciate the intention but it sounds pretty awkward}
Comment: 10,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot would never say something like that!
Comment: 10,0:16:42.42,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot taught me that a believing heart is my magic!
Comment: 10,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Comment: 10,0:17:18.96,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The blue moon apparition?
Comment: 10,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you create that fake Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you mocking me?
Comment: 10,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you come for?
Comment: 10,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to ask you.
Comment: 10,0:17:34.53,0:17:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you answer any question about the past, present, and future?
Comment: 10,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not everything.
Comment: 10,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that which I have no answer for
Comment: 10,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be answered by anyone else.
Comment: 10,0:17:51.66,0:17:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reveal my future to me!
Comment: 10,0:17:55.15,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really become a witch like Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How pointless.
Comment: 10,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more important to me than my life!
Comment: 10,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the future you wish for?
Comment: 10,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream...
Comment: 10,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter the gate.
Comment: 10,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This future can be yours.
Comment: 10,0:18:42.39,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in exchange for this radiant future, you will lose your past.
Comment: 10,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 10,0:18:49.76,0:18:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Grasping this future comes at a cost.
Comment: 10,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender your past.
Comment: 10,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Erase your unneeded past.
Comment: 10,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Comment: 10,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't erase it!
Comment: 10,0:19:30.16,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full of failures and mistakes I've made,\Nbut I don't want it to be erased! {I think it's too wordy}
Comment: 10,0:19:36.15,0:19:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? There is no value in retaining it.
Comment: 10,0:19:41.97,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The tears and frustration and laughter, they're all part of me!
Comment: 10,0:19:47.64,0:19:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my life, and it doesn't belong to anybody else!
Comment: 10,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived it as hard as I could!
Comment: 10,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't erase it!
Comment: 10,0:19:57.33,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain?
Comment: 10,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give up on becoming Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't!
Comment: 10,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard and become an amazing witch!{## aha, this is a bit different}
Comment: 10,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Professor told me.
Comment: 10,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is dreamed cannot be grasped.
Comment: 10,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But work towards it, day after day, \Nand you will find it in your hands!
Comment: 10,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Phaidoari...
Comment: 10,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Afairrynghor!
Comment: 10,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while.
Comment: 10,0:21:07.73,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a few years have passed since\Nwe last met, Professor Woodward.
Comment: 10,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the lost Claiomh Solais has been revived.
Comment: 10,0:21:23.36,0:21:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you were testing her.
Comment: 10,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you did of me.
Comment: 10,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's quite the stubborn one.
Comment: 10,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She revived a Word.
Comment: 10,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Phaidoari Afairrynghor.
Comment: 10,0:21:42.18,0:21:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko revived the first Word as well.
Comment: 10,0:21:47.21,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, she has also revived the second.
Comment: 10,0:21:52.67,0:21:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There are seven Words of Arcturus in total.
Comment: 10,0:21:57.65,0:22:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Revive the remaining Words.
Comment: 10,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You will aid her.
Comment: 10,0:22:19.77,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, I promise to tell you the truth one day.
